        <div class="tag">About us</div>
        <h2>Stuart and David Gilbert. A father and son workshop.</h2>
      </div>
      <p>Between us we have more than 75 years experience maintaining, repairing and servicing Land Rovers.</p>
      <p>Land Rovers have been at the heart of our working lives, and we take pride in keeping every vehicle performing exactly as it should &mdash; whether it's a family Discovery, a hard-working Defender, a cherished Range Rover, a Classic Range Rover or Series Land Rover.</p>
      <p>When you call, you will speak directly to <strong>Stuart or David</strong>. When you bring your vehicle in, it is one of us who will carry out the work. There are no receptionists, no service advisers and no middlemen. Just a father and son who care about doing the job properly.</p>
      <p class="sig">Stuart and David Gilbert, Orchards, Sittingbourne.</p>
